infos.value: ...Just as the report said. Not a Fennes soldier in sight.
It is as you say, Darling!
It's not only the Fennes soldiersâ€”Muraga and his subjects are nowhere to be found, either.
No one is here. Not the shinobi of Gouga, nor Dorando, nor Gargas...
Hey, now. This is enemy territory you're standing in.
Attempting to return to the Sanctum without a guard is a fool's errand.
Hmmm... Where, oh where, oh where is...?
Oh! I found him! Behind me all along, I see.
Heehee! A sweet press of your lips to mine as my prize, yes?
I don't recall offering any such thing.
This is the extent of Sadali's ill fortunes, is it?
Scatter these Sanctum scum to the winds and march on!
Our only objective is to behead Sadali!
